room_title: Escape room "The Real Kitchen Nightmare" by Esscape Room in New York
review: Raw & Real!  I've never seen an escape room in NYC with more atmosphere & ambience than the Kitchen Nightmare!

room_title: Escape room "The Real Kitchen Nightmare" by Esscape Room in New York
review: I absolutely loved this Kitchen Nightmare Esscape Room. It was very intense and difficult, but it definitely was a great experience. If you're looking for date ideas, I highly recommend it.Also, the Escape room is nearby Barroness Burger Bar which is great to grab food and drinks before and after :)
